item.title: Using the API
item.description: API and Integrations # Using the API # data.gouv.nc provides APIs to programmatically access datasets. You can use these APIs to integrate data into your applications or automate analysis. Example API request # GET https://data.gouv.nc/api/1/datasets/my-dataset
